Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.61,0:00:24.33,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s something I want to tell you, but it’s too heavy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:30.21,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like this, it seems I must break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:39.40,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many of these indescribable feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:46.24,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot deliver them to you, though you are near, the distance is great
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.05,0:00:55.06,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Forever only looking up at the blue sky is no good
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.06,0:01:02.29,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:09.70,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Unsteadily mustering strength, I want to try diving into your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.70,0:01:16.87,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning around (spinning around)…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:26.32,SR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightly floating, again today I am alone above the clouds
