Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:01.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s over. It’s over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go have some cake on the way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.65,0:02:05.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, shall we stop by El Cado?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We have room cleaning duty from today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.62,0:02:09.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that’s right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.22,0:02:10.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can’t go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.44,0:02:12.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They sell out so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:12.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see… I guess around here is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:19.80,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don’t run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m such a klutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.34,0:02:29.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let’s lock up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.05,0:02:42.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s somebody still in here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:46.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It won’t open!! Isn’t there anybody there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.52,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H121710&\bord0\fsp2\move(692,439,-57,439)\b1\fnLaskoner\fs72}Silence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.52,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s nobody…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Too high…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.64,0:03:03.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No good. I can’t get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.21,0:03:07.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,These things always happen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.98,0:03:12.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well, shouldn’t be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:14.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When club activities start,\Nsomebody will come…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:27.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s so tranquil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So mellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s making me… sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:45.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Evening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.73,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,All the clubs were off today!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:04.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to miss the\N“The Three Slashed” rerun
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,about the fake 10,000 bales of rice…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:09.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Yakumo is taping it…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:12.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I won’t be able\Nto do my homework either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:13.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I say tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:17.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,“I was locked up, so I couldn’t do it…”?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:22.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Yakumo doesn’t find the\Npudding I hid in the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:27.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Stop it!\NI’ve got to think positively!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:30.16,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I should use this situation effectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.49,0:04:31.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let’s see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:35.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How about imagining I’m marooned\Non a deserted island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:39.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll imagine I’m in an extreme situation…\NYes, I’m being tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll be my chance to verify\Nmy confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looking at it that way,\Nthis is becoming exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.91,0:04:47.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s see. Upon landing\Non a deserted island,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.75,0:04:49.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,what is the first thing I would do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.25,0:04:54.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Build a raft? Build a fire?\NNo, no, it has to be food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:58.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I’ll go look for\Ncoconuts or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:00.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Explore, explore… Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:06.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A pastry… Oh my, and I was only fooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, why is there a pastry\Nin a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Expiry date is the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s still fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:16.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, I’m hungry.\NI wonder if it’s okay to eat this…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.89,0:05:21.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! No matter how hungry,\Nsomeone threw this away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dange…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no will power…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:33.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.77,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning Extra Spicy Curry Pastry —\NSpicy enough to make your eyes spin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Ekthtra thpithy curry pathtry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate thpithy food! Geeth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:44.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Water! I want water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.51,0:05:49.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, what shall I do. There’s no\Nplumbing in here. This is true survival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:52.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Water! God, grant me rain!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A sprinkler?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.65,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Move, you…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.65,0:06:02.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What makes this move?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:04.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no switch…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My mouth’s still burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m getting irritated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:10.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:23.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Water, water, water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.81,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:30.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how castaways feel, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no change of clothes or towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:41.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn’t I think of something so ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:48.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think… what if I won’t\Nbe able to ever go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:54.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a little enjoyable… but, it’s sad\Nafter all. I wonder if Yakumo is worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.74,0:07:00.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And… I wonder what Karasuma is doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m having a hard time\Nsleeping… on this mat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:10.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Were you sleeping?\NI’m sorry for making such a commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:14.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Karasuma-kun, did you come to save me?!
