Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:36.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning duty… I forgot completely…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, let’s go to El Cado for cake\Non the way home after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:41.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the four of us… Huh?\NCome to think of it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.50,0:07:50.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’s Tsukamoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She cut out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:56.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Tsukamoto’s not the type\Nto cut out of something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:58.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably just forgot and went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:07:59.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:03.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She wanted to watch that\Nrerun of “The Three Slashed.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.18,0:08:06.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That sort of thing distracted her\Nand she just went on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:09.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, that girl is really hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:15.39,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. She went home? I was looking\Nforward to cleaning with Tenma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:16.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:19.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How unusual. He’s actually cleaning…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.31,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well, I would have been killing\Ntime until evening anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:35.24,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit. He could have set an earlier time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling me out again\Nwith a letter of challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t give up, do you Tennoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.96,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I crush you to pieces,\NI’ll keep on challenging you to fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.06,0:08:51.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:53.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,With a battle cry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fighting is weak,\Nbut your battle cry is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:57.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:08.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you’re in love with Tenma-chan,\NI’m showing no mercy. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Are you saying that you’re\Nin love with Tenma-chan, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard… don’t go calling her “chan”!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You… you’re wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NYou’re down, aren’t you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:26.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not the fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:30.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenm… I mean Tsukamoto-san, said\Nshe already has someone she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.11,0:09:33.83,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:37.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.54,0:09:40.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t make up stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s not a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:48.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. But I’m in\Nlove with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That… That can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:57.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I… I’ve never heard about this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.39,0:10:01.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Tenma-chan has someone… she likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:08.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and night fell, it was terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.94,0:10:10.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you didn’t go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.54,0:10:14.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn… Tenma-chan likes someone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s never shown a shred of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:22.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Who is the guy\Nthat Tenma-chan likes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:27.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to find that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:32.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The next problem is a little difficult, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.89,0:10:33.48,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Ma’am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:38.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The relation of energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,area, and speed at the perihelion where r,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:41.57,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The rate of variability is 0…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:43.33,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the guy that Tenma-chan likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.07,0:10:46.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… so that is the result.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.11,0:10:48.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a very precise answer.\NJust as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:52.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hanai is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:56.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he’s like seriousness clothed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Tenma-chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.09,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,… likes that serious guy, Hanai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:10.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, it can’t be. It’s just my hunch,\Nbut those aren’t the eyes of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:12.12,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:22.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?! No, it can’t be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:27.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.43,0:11:31.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it isn’t.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. Who in the world is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.99,0:11:41.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t keep up longer. This is bugging the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.95,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s Torimaru, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:46.45,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Harima mistakes the name “Karasuma” for “Torimaru.”\NThe kanjis are very similar, but differ by one stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:50.89,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He stares out the window\Nall day long. He’s strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:54.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he’s totally out of the running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:56.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That stupid and faintly dull boy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:12:01.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn’t even have a one percent chance\nof taking my Tenma-chan’s heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:04.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re a good guy… er… Torimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, tell me, Tenma-chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.79,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She’s looking my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the eyes of love?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:15.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:17.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.58,0:12:32.77,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.92,0:12:39.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:45.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:49.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be! That burning look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:53.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I kind of thought so, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:02.20,note,,0000,0000,0000,,Flag: Congratulations Kenji Harima.\NI am wonderful. November 2004, Lucky day
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:13:02.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan’s in love with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice but to confess now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:13.61,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Tenma-chan. I’ve never cursed\Nbeing so thickheaded as I have today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:21.56,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That delicate body burning\Nin love, waiting each day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:24.23,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been harsh.\NIt must have been difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But that’s all over now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:29.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Tenma-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.57,0:13:35.33,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You don’t have to say anything.\NRight now, I will tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:41.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.25,0:13:39.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(476,433)}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:43.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFFFFF&\t(2000,3776,\1c&HFCFCFC&)\3c&H141315&\t(2000,3776,\3c&HFCFCFC&)\4c&H141315&\t(2000,3776,\4c&HFCFCFC&)\fad(0,1932)\frz0\t(0,3790,\frz2160\move(476,433,98,107))\clip(m 231 297 l 236 289 241 292 247 267 249 288 257 263 265 269 273 282 283 300 282 289 254 250 248 228 237 209 226 199 217 195 200 187 170 186 143 197 123 221 116 236 19 248 2 12 528 16 531 191 618 194 620 289 632 483 196 483 218 384 260 366 295 354 316 345 328 334 342 331 331 326 336 312 326 317 329 301 316 315 313 301 307 320 296 311 296 325 258 331 239 328 228 320)}I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.51,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\c&HF5FAF5&\t(0,1000,\c&H4C534C&)\frz354\pos(484,203)\frx12\fry18}Yagami Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.51,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.5\shad0\c&HF5FAF5&\t(0,1000,\c&HF3F6EC&)\3c&HF5FAF5&\t(0,1000,\3c&H7F8981&)\frz354\frx12\fry18\pos(487,198)}Yagami Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.25,0:13:48.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’ll take ten days for you to recover…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:54.43,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like something really great happened today, but I can’t remember what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:58.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,However, someone with\Nas bad luck as you is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:01.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My memory is spotty…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:04.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess for an\Naccident as bad as that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:07.91,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,complete recovery in ten days\Nis actually pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:14.37,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, I came to see how you were doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:17.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Why? Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\bord1\be1\shad1\fs40\fnAirstream\c&HF1F7FF&\3c&H010344&\pos(519,71)}Mokkori
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscy100\fsp-1\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fnImpact\fs72\b0\i0\c&H1A16DF&\pos(524,111)}{\fscy112}F{\fscy88}ansub
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.96,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord1.2\be1\shad2\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs26\i1\c&HAE690B&\fnFranklin Gothic Demi\fscy115\pos(525,127)}www.mokkori.cz
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.92,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima-kun, I came to see how you were doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Why? Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.72,0:14:30.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Osakabe-sensei, hello.\NAre you here to visit as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Harima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:35.68,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… I-I’m fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not fine! A white hospital room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m in pajamas! Tenma-chan in\Nplain clothes carrying flowers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:46.11,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on? My heart’s pounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:49.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s so easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.15,0:14:50.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukamoto-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:55.26,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you just came, but can\Nyou arrange those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.42,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:04.36,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can finally breathe, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it myself, but I’m pitiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.37,0:15:12.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m in the way. I’m disappearing, Kenji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:14.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha… What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay, please stay, Itoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.88,0:15:19.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m hopeless alone, I can’t do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you’re being cowardly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.55,0:15:22.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.88,0:15:25.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you call someone, remember the “San”.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:28.82,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,San… Itoko-san! Don’t abandon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:33.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was abandoning you?\NRelax. I have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.46,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:37.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,An intercom I made myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:38.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Intercom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:45.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll give you conversational advice,\Nso you can just follow along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:48.03,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s a good thing this hospital allows mobile phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.76,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are lucky after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:53.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to put on\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:54.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not forcing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.62,0:15:56.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.08,0:15:57.99,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you asked, I have to comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:16:00.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on the collar of your\Npajamas and this in your ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.53,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s just like a detective’s. Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:06.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she make these as a hobby?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best. See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:17.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:20.44,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Tsukamoto-kun’s coming back.\NAre you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:21.47,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:23.78,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:24.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:26.70,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:27.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a terrible accident.\NI was so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:33.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’m glad you’re fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.89,0:16:34.91,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.91,0:16:36.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:40.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I brought some black tea. Can I brew some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.40,0:16:42.38,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:43.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:45.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:51.07,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,They’re only tea bags, but it tastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.07,0:16:54.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s better if the water is freshly boiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.11,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,I like black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:59.41,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I like black tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.97,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? That’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.36,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re shaped for easy childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.36,0:17:10.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re shaped for easy childbirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.38,0:17:11.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:16.86,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24\fad(0,300)\q2}Note: In Japan, women who have big bottoms are said to have\Neasier childbirth. It “is” a compliment, although very embarassing,\Nand so only old people use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:15.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you making me say!\NCan you see it too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s the first time\Nanyone said that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.30,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart’s pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.86,0:17:29.98,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re alone! She came to see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:34.44,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Tenma-chan in plain clothes\Nlooks three times cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:36.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I’m glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:43.62,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you’re sort of a delinquent,\Nand I wasn’t sure if flowers were okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.58,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.28,0:17:48.06,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers are important to a delinquent, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:50.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ah… Is… Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:52.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s a flower like you, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:55.20,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Is what you really want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.40,0:18:00.54,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, how come you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:05.27,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m… No, rather, I can’t say\Nsomething that embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:08.85,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NShe came just to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.56,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to say something sensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.85,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.02,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Relay your feelings frankly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:15.86,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s a basic of successful love.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:18.35,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh… I… I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.53,0:18:21.32,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, I’ll say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:25.25,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,A flower like you, that is! {I did some changes due to WF subs, check it and decide what would you prefer}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.75,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:36.38,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs24\fad(0,300)}Note: “Kimi mitai” means “like you” referring to the flowers beautiful like you. However, Tenma in all her intelligence interpreted “kimi” as “egg yolk”, the alternative meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:36.38,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s like a yolk? Is it a story\Nabout eggs? What happens next?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.18,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah… No, there used to\Nbe ice cream like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:44.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The texture was just like\Nthe yolk of a hard boiled egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:48.19,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she be so thickheaded!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.15,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It took everything I had to say it\Nand this is what I get!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:54.66,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma Tsukamoto cannot\Nconnect conversations
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:57.11,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,when there is more than\N10 seconds in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.57,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But really, you actually\Nsaid something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:03.25,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:05.67,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.67,0:19:09.34,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenji can’t make those connections either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.68,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:17.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Go carefully. Tsukamoto is frighteningly\Nslow when it comes to attention from men.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.05,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in class there should be\Nmany boys interested in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:21.04,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in class there should be\Nmany boys interested in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:25.01,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoko! Tell me their names later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:30.69,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, don’t panic.\NEverything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:33.20,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, you are one step ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.20,0:19:34.87,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You are about the only one who is able to\Nsay something so embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.21,0:19:42.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, embarrassing. Very embarrassing.\NReally embarrassing…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.78,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoko, there’s something\Nthat’s bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:50.29,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not really just having\Nfun at my expense, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:56.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I’m suddenly getting interference!\NI’m going to stop transmitting for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.22,0:19:58.21,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Wha… What’s that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.13,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Farewell, Kenji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:01.99,SR second,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoko! Hey! Ito…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.60,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:07.40,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll have to do this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:09.64,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:12.10,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry, the apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.40,0:20:17.21,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What, is that all?! It’s okay.\NI got some from Itoko a little while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.70,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s just enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.70,0:20:20.86,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You ate some earlier? Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.08,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.45,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just hungry for half an apple!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:31.04,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh! I don’t know what\NI’m saying myself! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.71,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s laughing at me! Oh, no,\Ndid I do something wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.17,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.44,0:20:46.51,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,We sit right next to each other,\Nbut we haven’t talked before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.74,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s good we talked about\Nall kind of things today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.14,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.45,0:20:59.22,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That’s so. Now that\Nyou mention it, it’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:04.72,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I went out of my way\Nand depended on Itoko for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:06.78,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had to be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:10.63,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it’s not too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.63,0:21:12.66,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be frank! Frank…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.73,0:21:16.00,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hug you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:18.90,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:33.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want Tsukamoto-kun, she left while you were thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:35.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,She said to take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:40.94,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it’s Tsukamoto-kun.\NThe one you love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.94,0:21:43.50,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:54.37,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys are always chasing after girls
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:22:00.40,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,All day long they’re thinking of girls
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:04.83,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,But those boys certainly are a little stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.83,0:22:10.30,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,They never seem to understand girls’ feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:14.92,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you really really are a big dummy
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:17.59,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I give you a lesson, Big Dummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:21.08,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the most important thing in the world is…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.01,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that absolutely must be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.01,0:22:28.27,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s definitely “timing”, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:31.41,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,So, if you wanna say “I love you”,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.60,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on a date, or do something…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.28,0:22:40.61,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, kiss, or say goodbye, at any time…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:44.62,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the most important thing in the world is
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.62,0:22:49.53,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,definitely “timing”, I think, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:50.51,SR ED,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.55,0:23:09.02,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher told Yakumo to go and look.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:10.88,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Is our class so untrustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:15.55,SR main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on School Rumble, “Cleaning The Pool!\NRunning Around The Pool! War At The Pool!”
